    "lethal":        { example: "Even a small error in dosage can turn a beneficial medicine into a lethal substance.", exampleJa: "投与量のわずかなエラーでさえ、有益な薬を致死的な物質に変えることができる。" },
    "litigation":    { example: "The two companies settled to avoid costly litigation that could have dragged on for years.", exampleJa: "2社は何年も続く可能性のある高価な訴訟を避けるために和解した。" },
